Boy Frank, do I ever agree with you about Coast to Coast.  Used to listen to it but no more.  I like Jeff Rense's programming much better.

Sumption Frank <fsumption@...> wrote:               I can�t image anyone on the other side wanting, or expecting us to work for Art Bell, talk about someone that�s negative! Art�s whole thing is to try to twist everything to the dark side. It�s the same with everyone on Coast to Coast, they try to make it all as scary, and fear based as possible. That voice I got was probably from the darkheads, everything else on that tape was. I finally gave up on it, and ran another session last night. 
  
      
---------------------------------
  
  From: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com [mailto:EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of Misty Dawn
Sent: Monday, June 19, 2006 1:19 PM
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] Voice about Art Bell.

  
          I hear that exactly as you do. That made me dig out one of mine. They were talking about art but when I was listening i heard "its oliver (all over) misty come closer to art work of art" and in my mind I was thinking art/painting/craft aka images not art bell LOL so had to dig it out to see if thats still what i hear thru the fuzz.

    

    The image group and the regular evp group communicate in different ways so I still think they meant images, however they have been trying to get me to move out of this neighborhood but I am not moving closer to art bell. Have a friend from there and the food is a little too strange for me LOL.

    

    Misty

    

    

Sumption Frank <fsumption@...> wrote:

            Hi All;

     I found this on the second listening of the June 5th tape, I don�t know how I missed the first time through. This is the stuff that confuses me to no end, I get all this bogus prophecy crap, as if something wants to discredit the boxes, then I get this kind of voice. I did put this on my site.  http://franksumption.tripod.com/id144.html

     Frank
